1. What is devOps?

Process of improving the application  delivery ,  by ensuring there is  proper automation , quality , continous monitoring & Continous Testing 
#############################################
2. Why DevOps ? 

Before 10 years 
Sys Admin - He was Creating Server on VMware/ OpenStack 
Build and Release Engineer - He Deploys the application on the server that the developer has built 
Server Admin - used to create app servers 

for delivering all these , so many roles were involved , application delivery was taking longer time due to manual effort. 

To improve the above process of delivery , devops has come to place 
#############################################

Introduce yourself - 

m working as a DevOps for past 3 Years , Before that I was working as Linux Admin

I take care of automation , ensuring quality in application , setup continous monitroing 